    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the new-car price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it still runs like a dream! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale, so I've priced it to move!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
