      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care. The exterior finish still holds a deep, impressive shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is free of tears or heavy stains, and the interior retains a fresh, non-smoker scent. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is solid\u2014it starts promptly, idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts without hesitation. It has been serviced regularly, with recent brake work and a fresh oil change already completed. This is a reliable, attractive car that has many miles of enjoyment left to offer.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
